(30, 'Thermo-mechanical characterization of multi-walled carbon nanotube reinforced polycarbonate composites: A molecular dynamics approach', 'S Sharma, R Chandra, P Kumar, N Kumar', 'The present study aims at examining the mechanical properties of multi-walled carbon nanotubesâ€“polycarbonate composites (MWCNTâ€“PC), through a molecular dynamics (MD) simulation.', 'http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1631072115000418', '2015-05-23 14:47:21'),
(31, 'Contention Aware Energy Efficient Scheduling on Heterogeneous Multiprocessors', 'J Singh, S Betha, B Mangipudi, N Auluck', 'Energy efficiency along with enhanced performance are two important goals of scheduling on multiprocessors.', 'http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpls/abs_all.jsp?arnumber=6811172&tag=1', '2015-05-23 14:50:09'),
(32, 'Infrared Thermal Wave Imaging for Nondestructive Testing of Fibre Reinforced Polymers', 'JA Siddiqui, V Arora, R Mulaveesala, A Muniyappa', 'Among various widely used InfraRed Thermal Non-Destructive Testing (IRTNDT) modalities, Non-Stationary Thermal Wave Imaging (NSTWI) techniques have proved to be an indispensable approach for the inspection and evaluation of various materials.', 'http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s11340-015-0019-z', '2015-05-23 14:50:58'),
(33, 'On a conjecture of ErdÅ‘s and certain Dirichlet series', 'T Chatterjee, M Murty', 'Let f : Z/qZâ†’Z be such that f(a) = Â±1 for 1 â‰¤ a < q, and f(q) = 0. Then Erdos conjectured that Ë P nâ‰¥1 f(n)/n 6= 0. For q even, it is easy to show that the conjecture is true. The case q â‰¡ 3 (mod 4) was solved by Murty and Saradha.', 'http://www.mast.queensu.ca/~murty/Tapas-Murty-ErdosConj-2.pdf', '2015-05-23 14:53:20'),
(34, 'Potassium Induced Stitching of Flexible Tripodal Ligand into Bi-metallic Two-dimensional Coordination Polymer for Photo-degradation of Organic Dyes', 'VK Bhardwaj', 'A novel strategy for the stitching of a tripodal ligand into a bi-metallic two-dimensional (2D) coordination polymer has been reported.', 'http://pubs.rsc.org/en/content/articlehtml/2015/dt/c5dt01215e', '2015-05-23 14:54:11');
